pageContext.claim: “He [Biden] destroyed your [auto] industry. But I brought it back....A vote for Biden is a vote to extinguish, demolish and wipe out Michigan's auto industry and many of your other industries, many of your other industries.”
pageContext.analysis: This is absurd. The Obama-Biden administration, working with the outgoing George W. Bush administration, extended billions of dollars in loans that rescued the auto industry during the Great Recession. Trump did not bring anything back.
